                                                                                                                                                                             PS
                                                                                                                                                               HS-PS4-4
WAVES AND THEIR APPLICATIONS
                                                            Evaluate the validity and reliability of claims in published materials regarding the effects that different frequencies
             Performance Expectation                        of electromagnetic radiation have when absorbed by matter.
                                                            Emphasis is on the idea that photons associated with different frequencies of light have different energies, and
                                                            the damage to living tissue from electromagnetic radiation depends on the energy of the radiation. Examples of
              Clarification Statement                       published materials could include trade books, magazines, web resources, videos, and other passages that may
                                                            reflect bias. Emphasis is on qualitative descriptions.
