                                                                    1
                                    CONNECTIONS TO ELA & MATH
K.OA.A.4 For any number from 1 to 9, find the number that makes 10
when added to the given number, e.g., by using objects or drawings,
and record the answer with a drawing or equation.
K.OA.A.5 Fluently add and subtract within 5.
1.OA.A.1 Use addition and subtraction within 20 to solve word
problems involving situations of adding to, taking from, putting
together, taking apart, and comparing, with unknowns in all positions
(e.g., by using objects, drawings, and equations with a symbol for the
unknown number to represent the problem).
1.MD.C.4 Organize, represent, and interpret data with up to three
categories; ask and answer questions about the total number of
