Appendix A: Learning Progression
       SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING PRACTICES                                                                                               2
       CROSSCUTTING CONCEPTS                                                                                                          10
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: PHYSICAL SCIENCE - MATTER AND ITS INTERACTIONS (PS1)                                                  14
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: PHYSICAL SCIENCE – MOTION AND STABILITY: FORCES AND INTERACTIONS (PS2)                                16
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: PHYSICAL SCIENCE – ENERGY (PS3)                                                                       18
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: PHYSICAL SCIENCE – WAVES AND THEIR APPLICATIONS (PS4)                                                 21
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: LIFE SCIENCE – FROM MOLECULES TO ORGANISMS: STRUCTURES AND PROCESSES (LS1)                            23
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: LIFE SCIENCE – ECOSYSTEMS: INTERACTIONS, ENERGY, AND DYNAMICS (LS2)                                   26
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: LIFE SCIENCE – HEREDITY: INHERITANCE AND VARIATION OF TRAITS (LS3)                                    29
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: LIFE SCIENCE – BIOLOGICAL EVOLUTION: UNITY AND DIVERSITY (LS4)                                        31
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: EARTH AND SPACE SCIENCE – EARTH’S PLACE IN THE UNIVERSE (ESS1)                                        34
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: EARTH AND SPACE SCIENCE – EARTH’S SYSTEMS (ESS2)                                                      36
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: EARTH AND SPACE SCIENCE – HUMAN SUSTAINABILITY (ESS3)                                                 40
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE – RESOURCES AND RESOURCE MANAGEMENT (EVS1)                                      42
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE – ENVIRONMENTAL AWARENESS AND PROTECTION (EVS2)                                 43
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE – PERSONAL RESPONSIBILITIES (EVS3)                                              44
       DISCIPLINARY CORE IDEAS: ENGINEERING, TECHNOLOGY AND APPLICATIONS TO SCIENCE – ENGINEERING DESIGN (ETS1)                       45
