             Performance Expectation                    Use observations to describe patterns of what plants and animals (including humans) need to survive.
                                                        Examples of patterns could include that plants make their own food while animals do not, the different kinds of
              Clarification Statement                   food needed by different types of animals, the requirement of plants to have light, or that all living things need water.
